6078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"幫推  借位一用<br />\n<br />\n我呼籲 政治人物 校長 社工 行入去警總叫曾經濫捕 拳打腳踢 插贓 嘅警察自首<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1736095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1736095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老鼠曾<br />\n<br />\n如果你地唔夠膽咁做 根本係雙重標準<br />\n乜撚野中學校長都只係助紂為虐<br />\n我屌你 再你埋你間中學<br />\n<br />\n重可以有隨行傳媒同假傳媒跟住入去<br />\n<br />\n藍衫可以先摘名 記低UI<br />\n白衫就要捉住遊街 公審<br />\n<br />\n但校長 社工可以確保佢唔被濫用暴力 虐打<br />\n享有呢d本身香港基本法已經清楚寫明 每個人都有嘅莊嚴承諾嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n題外話 <br />\n雙普選都係基本法清楚寫明 每個人都有嘅莊嚴承諾嘅權利<br />\n但都唔知去咗邊到"},{"pid":"97041da045445ecbbedcccf3a6d8239c822a23f1","tid":1736464,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:02:05.000Z","msg":"so many <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nif he can."},{"pid":"c1b3b6d7d824dd42c31674304b5634f88d799d43","tid":1736464,"uid":3212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"隻燥狂曱甴都係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6db9ece8ca44632dc3f17f5aef45dc6e371ab69","tid":1736464,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"關佢x事"},{"pid":"406d11ef12ffdd856921f9b0839a3a5a094be68c","tid":1736464,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"又叫班細既走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dab83533a98ec447cc273a5c8e1a5b227f97d54","tid":1736464,"uid":33686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"佢入去想做咩 視察？"},{"pid":"6bdcc61609ea458533cb81c2a81f828c71